reviews.title: Great app
reviews.comment: Extremely user friendly and intuitive!
reviews.author: Nolan Emmer

reviews.title: Excellent
reviews.comment: Very cool will definitely make it much easier and faster to rent a car
reviews.author: ari schwartz

reviews.title: Great!
reviews.comment: So excited National finally has an app!  I travel with business and this is going to make life so much easier.  From what I have seen so far, the app looks great and I am impressed!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Doesn\'t work
reviews.comment: I login, select make a reservation, choose my airport, then it asks me to login again, which I do. I am then kicked back to the main screen to start the cycle all over again. I\'m rather stunned that this was not noticed prior to its release...
reviews.author: Beth Peeples

reviews.title: I have been waiting for this forever!
reviews.comment: Very nicely done, I\'m glad National finally has an app to help me with managing travel through them. I only rent from National if they are available.
reviews.author: Devon Abblitt

reviews.title: Great app.. Worth waiting for!
reviews.comment: As a frequent traveler and Emerald Club member, I\'ve been waiting for this app for a while. It was worth the wait.. Very slick, intuitive. Creating and managing reservations (even extending) is easier and better than using the website!
reviews.author: Elizabeth L

reviews.title: Greatest cat rental app!!!!
reviews.comment: Way better than using the Web is about time!!
reviews.author: John Flores

reviews.title: Looks great for first release
reviews.comment: Good Android look/feel to it. It certainly is slow to download my information though and seems like it has to wait to download updates BOTH when starting the app and then when looking at other pages. It\'d also be great if I could change rental return locations within the app. When travel plans change, it\'d be great to be able to do everything on the go.
reviews.author: Allan Klein

reviews.title: Horrible
reviews.comment: National should of held off until it was much better. Ugly interface, things dont work, cant do much. What were they thinking!
reviews.author: Renato Delatorre

reviews.title: Smooth
reviews.comment: The app is really smooth and, while some features are \"coming soon\", it does exactly what you need without issue.  Great job National.
reviews.author: Jared Reno

reviews.title: Emerald Club Friendly?
reviews.comment: The App looks great! But wherr to you enter your Emerald Club Info??
reviews.author: KYNG ME

reviews.title: Travel made easy!
reviews.comment: This is going to make my life so much eaasier!
reviews.author: Michael Burke

reviews.title: More than just an optimized website
reviews.comment: Follows you through the whole transaction, from reservation to rental to return. Easy to use interface. Look forward to future enhancements like past rental receipts and Virtual Aisle (most anticipated of all - choose a car at locations that do not have full Aisle service).
reviews.author: Jason Haws

reviews.title: Well-made.
reviews.comment: A solid car rental app.
reviews.author: David Henry

reviews.title: Login broken!
reviews.comment: App works fine except when I login with my emerald club account and details of my existing reservations - the app terminates unexpectedly and closes. Would have rated this above average if that works
reviews.author: Jeffrey Garaygay

reviews.title: About time...
reviews.comment: I was seriously getting annoyed at national for the crappy website and lack of an app. App is now nicer than the website. Good job, finally.
reviews.author: Wes Wu

reviews.title: Less than beta quality
reviews.comment: Push notifications, exit app prompt, yuck. Many features have buttons but aren\'t yet enabled nor \"optimized for mobile\".
reviews.author: Erik Larson

reviews.title: I love this new app
reviews.comment: I love this new app. ..
reviews.author: Lorenzo Johnson

reviews.title: Works Great!
reviews.comment: Very easy.
reviews.author: Kevin Gaddy

reviews.title: Excellent
reviews.comment: Awesome app. Will make traveling much easier.
reviews.author: Patrick Gribbon
